      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.BufferedTransformer<T>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.BufferedTransformer-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A transformer that decouples its upstream and downstream stages using a bounded\n<xref href=\"System.Threading.Channels.Channel%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>, enabling pipeline parallelism: the upstream stage can run ahead\nwhile the downstream stage consumes, instead of being lock-stepped by\n<xref href=\"System.Collections.Generic.IAsyncEnumerable%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>'s pull model.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.CastTransformer-2.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.CastTransformer-2.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.CastTransformer<TSource, TDestination>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.CastTransformer-2.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A transformer that casts each input item to <code class=\"typeparamref\">TDestination</code>, throwing\n<xref href=\"System.InvalidCastException\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> if any item is not of that type.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.ChainTransformer-3.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.ChainTransformer-3.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.ChainTransformer<TSource, TIntermediate, TDestination>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.ChainTransformer-3.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Combines two transformers into a single transformer: items flow through the first,\nthen through the second, with the intermediate type erased from the chain's public\nsignature.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.ChainTransformerWithCancellation-3.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.ChainTransformerWithCancellation-3.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.ChainTransformerWithCancellation<TSource, TIntermediate, TDestination>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.ChainTransformerWithCancellation-3.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Combines two cancellation-aware transformers into a single\n<xref href=\"Wolfgang.Etl.Abstractions.ITransformWithCancellationAsync%602\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>: items flow through\nthe first, then through the second, and a single <xref href=\"System.Threading.CancellationToken\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> supplied\nto the chain is propagated to both stages.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
