      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.ChunkTransformer<T>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.ChunkTransformer-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A transformer that batches the input sequence into fixed-size groups and yields each batch as\na single <xref href=\"System.Collections.Generic.IReadOnlyList%601\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> output item.</p>\n"
    },
