      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.DistinctByTransformer<TSource, TKey>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.DistinctByTransformer-2.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A transformer that yields each input item with a unique key, where the key is produced by a\ncaller-supplied selector. Subsequent items whose key has already been seen are dropped.</p>\n"
    },
