      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.DistinctTransformer-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A transformer that yields each unique item from the input sequence, dropping subsequent\nduplicates.</p>\n"
    },
