      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.ProgressReportingTransformer<T>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.ProgressReportingTransformer-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A decorator transformer that calls a user-supplied callback for each item as it passes\nthrough, then yields the item unchanged. Useful for reporting progress, logging, or\ncollecting metrics on any stage in a composed pipeline.</p>\n"
    },
