      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.SelectManyTransformer-2.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A transformer that projects each input item to a sequence of zero or more output items\nand yields the concatenation of all those sequences.</p>\n"
    },
