      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.TakeWhileTransformer<T>",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Wolfgang.Etl.Transformers.TakeWhileTransformer-1.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A transformer that yields items from the start of the input sequence as long as a\ncaller-supplied predicate returns <a href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/csharp/language-reference/builtin-types/bool\">true</a>; the first item that fails\nthe predicate stops enumeration immediately and is not yielded.</p>\n"
    },
